				<td colspan="2"><span>Okay, I Dinged 50 last night, and hope to be 51 before the end of the weekend (maybe nothing is set in stone).  Anyhow, I would like to know from 51 to 65 if you had to do it over again, how would you recommend, how did you do AA points and in what disiplines?  Let me tell you what I've been told. All AA exp is getting exp like lvl 51, just get your basic stuff go to lvl 61 and get all the AA you can then work your way up to 65.  Another I've heard is at 51 do 90% AA and 10% Exp get all the AA you want for the General move up to 55, do the same thing and so forth.  Are there really good ones? really useless ones?  Are there any web sites that really tell you all this?  I posted this here cause it will allow other to look forward and be able to plan ahead if they wish.</span></td>
